text: Kyzyl-Chishma () is a rural locality (a village) in Miyakinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 178 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 4 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Kyzyl-Chishma, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
